Embroidery, the ancient art has increased people's life interests and influenced human's sentiment for thousands of years. Chinese embroidery, as one of the founders of this art, always takes the lead condition in this profession. Chinese embroidery artistes keep searching new techniques of embroidery continuously, developing new art style, and finally brings embroidery art to the new altitude at last century. They exploit the new area of embroidery, embroidered realistically. People highly praised classic paint such as "Monalisa" and "Sunflower" that embroidered by artistes. Beside this, artistes embroidered animals, flowers, and birds lifelikely.
Chinese embroideries are often sent to the country leaders who visit China as national gifts. Those country leaders including George Bush, the President of the United States, the royal family of Japan and Annam, the Former Secretary-General of the United Nations, etc. With the popularization of embroidery, this art become peoples' favorites at various countries. An increasing number of people regard it as top grade collection and decoration.

Han-Tang Suzhou embroidery workshop established for the purpose of spreading Chinese traditional embroidery art, extending national embroidery articles. We believe these fantastic embroidery articles displayed in the website will make you love this art. If you want buy some of them, please visit our website (http://www.dufe-emba.com/works.htm).
